select count(*) from investor where isDeleted = 0

select count(*) from Profile where SystemCode = 'OP' and isdeleted = 0

select count(*) from UserHistory where UserId = ${#Project#createdUserId} and UpdatedDateTimeUtc >= '2016-01-01 00:00:00.000' and UpdatedDateTimeUtc <= '2020-01-01 00:00:00.000'

select count(*) from ( select a.Id as UserAccessHistoryId, b.* from UserAccessHistory as a, UserAccessRoleDetailHistory as b where a.UserAccessId = b.UserAccessId and a.UserId = ${#Project#createdUserId} and b.UpdatedDateTimeUtc >= '2016-01-01 00:00:00.000' and b.UpdatedDateTimeUtc <= '2020-01-01 00:00:00.000' union select c.Id as UserAccessHistoryId, d.* from UserAccessHistory as c, UserAccessPermissionSetDetailHistory as d where c.UserAccessId = d.UserAccessId and c.UserId = ${#Project#createdUserId} and d.UpdatedDateTimeUtc >= '2016-01-01 00:00:00.000' and d.UpdatedDateTimeUtc <= '2020-01-01 00:00:00.000' ) as temp

select count(*) from UserAccess as access, UserAccessRoleDetail as roleDetail, DataScopeDetailDeltaHistory as scopeDetailHistory where access.Id = roleDetail.UserAccessId and roleDetail.DataScopeId = scopeDetailHistory.DataScopeId and access.UserId = ${#Project#createdUserId} and scopeDetailHistory.UpdatedDateTimeUtc >= '2016-01-01 00:00:00.000' and scopeDetailHistory.UpdatedDateTimeUtc <= '2020-01-01 00:00:00.000'

select count(*) from UserAccess as access, UserAccessPermissionSetDetail as permissionSetDetail, DataScopeDetailDeltaHistory as scopeDetailHistory where access.Id = permissionSetDetail.UserAccessId and permissionSetDetail.DataScopeId = scopeDetailHistory.DataScopeId and access.UserId = ${#Project#createdUserId} and scopeDetailHistory.UpdatedDateTimeUtc >= '2016-01-01 00:00:00.000' and scopeDetailHistory.UpdatedDateTimeUtc <= '2020-01-01 00:00:00.000'
